<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Welcome to Mini Blog</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .btn:hover { background: #0056b3; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎉 Welcome to Mini Blog!</h1>
      <p>Your journey as a blogger starts now</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.email %>,</h2>
      
      <p>Welcome to Mini Blog! We're excited to have you join our community of writers and readers.</p>
      
      <h3>What you can do now:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>📝 Create your first blog post</li>
        <li>💬 Comment on other posts</li>
        <li>🔍 Discover amazing content</li>
        <li>👥 Connect with other writers</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Ready to get started? Click the button below to sign in and create your first post!</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @login_url %>" class="btn">Sign In & Start Writing</a>
      </div>
      
      <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
      
      <h3>Getting Started Tips:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Write your first post:</strong> Share your thoughts, ideas, or stories</li>
        <li><strong>Engage with the community:</strong> Read and comment on other posts</li>
        <li><strong>Build your audience:</strong> Publish regularly and interact with readers</li>
      </ol>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
      
      <p>Happy blogging!<br>
      The Mini Blog Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %> because you signed up for Mini Blog.</p>
      <p>If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 